nodes.text: Versatile Humanoid Biped Units were multipedal locomotion parts for droids. They were typical protocol bipedal units equipped with walking, running, and jumping ability. They were made of copper, titanium and high-carbon steel, which allowed them to be magnetic. They had medium-to-low material durability. The Versatile Humanoid Biped Units were designed by Cybot Galactica and were part of the famous 3PO-series, and presumably others like 3PX-series or TC-series.
